      "file_path": "models-pap/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/models/pap/PdpSubGroup.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 44,
      "message": "yes PAP is the authority. But PAP can tell the minInstanceCount to Kubernetes. And Kubernetes has to anytime maintain that number of instances running (which is referred as currentInstanceCount). Ideally, currentInstanceCount = minInstanceCount.\n\nAlso, this field is only applicable for GET requests.",
